      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "四青袍、白俭同上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00002",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "身受皇恩，与黎民，判断冤情。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00003",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "山上青松山下花，青松罩定涧中花。待等八月秋风起，只见青松不见花。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00004",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "下官，白俭。官居南乐县正堂。自到任以来，官清民顺，四方安靖。今当三六九日，放告之期。左右，将放告牌抬出。",
      "text_length": 52
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00005",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "二衙役"
      ],
      "text": "是。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00006",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "二衙役同抬牌。张聪、庄子同上。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00007",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "张聪",
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "冤枉！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00008",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "二衙役"
      ],
      "text": "启太爷：外面有人喊冤。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00009",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "带进来。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00010",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张聪"
      ],
      "text": "叩见太爷。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00011",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "张聪跪。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00012",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
