        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "是啊，他出家人本有座位。但不知你所告何事？你叫什么？",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00020",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张聪"
      ],
      "text": "小人名叫张聪，字骷髅，北乡人氏。是我去到威县要帐回来，身带银钱包裹，行至松林之内，偶尔困倦，打睡一时，不想被这道人，将我的银钱包裹窃去，故尔前来投告，望太爷作主。",
      "text_length": 81
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00021",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "那一道家，你为何窃取他的包裹？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00022",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "我乃出家之人，两手空空，何曾见他的包裹呀！",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00023",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张聪"
      ],
      "text": "启太爷，他们出家之人，惯会妖术邪法，将小人的包裹隐藏起来，也是有的。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00024",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "是呀，你们出家之人，惯会邪术，隐藏他的包裹也是有的。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00025",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "若论邪术，贫道却也略知一二。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00026",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "来，将他座位撤去。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00027",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "为何撤去座位？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00028",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "本县好意与你讲话，你为何口出大言？",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00029",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "非是贫道口出大言，纵然会用邪术，定要到那大户人家偷盗，金银财帛任我搬取，又何必劫他行路单人？",
      "text_length": 46
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00030",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "张聪"
      ],
      "text": "太爷休听他胡言，不动大刑，谅他不招认。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00031",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "张聪，我把你这畜生呀！",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00032",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "小张聪生来命运低，一心要穿锦绣衣。绫罗缎匹任你取，一心又想美貌妻。二八佳人陪伴你，你一心又想作官职。七品郎官你作起，小官又怕大官欺。当朝太宰封了你，你一心又想作皇帝。万里江山让与你，你一心又想上天梯。上天梯儿高搭起，一心又想作玉帝。金童玉女服侍你，你岂不怕那五雷殛。阴阳宝扇扇化了你，",
      "text_length": 142
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00033",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "又只见白骨满堂飞。想必是冤家作了对，吓得我三魂七魄飞。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00034",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "为何一时他化做白骨一堆？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00035",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "也是他命该如此，他前生欠下强盗银钱，今生才被强盗把他财帛夺去，将他杀害，是我救了他的性命，他贪心不足，恩将仇报，以至如此，就请大檀越用棺木一口，将他尸骨装敛，埋在西门以外，大路傍边，立一碑碣，上写张聪之墓，日后也好叫他家中人搬取。",
      "text_length": 115
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00036",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "来，照法办来。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00037",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "二衙役同抬尸骨。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00038",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "他既然应死，你为何将他带在本县堂上？",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00039",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "带他前来，无非是化你一口棺木。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00040",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "你竟自化到我堂上来了么？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00041",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "不化东，不化西，单化一只白公鸡。红头黑尾黄肚皮，连毛秤来二斤一。一口吞腹内，还在腹中不住啼。归来归来，三人同穿一只鞋。莫说鞋儿小，三人同穿穿不了。丢了好，丢了好，丢了你的烦恼少，不丢你就少烦恼。舍了罢，舍了罢，舍了你的造化大，不舍你的大造化。",
      "text_length": 121
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00042",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "哦！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00043",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "他那里言和语我全然不晓，参禅妙语甚蹊跷。走上前来施礼到，望祈仙师说根苗。",
      "text_length": 36
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00044",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "弟子要求仙师将道法传授一二。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00045",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "道法高，道法高，妖魔鬼怪望风逃。为人去了七情欲，方能不被火来烧。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00046",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "仙师此去，弟子要送你一程。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00047",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "我本飘飘一地仙，终日云游在外边。行踪缥渺终无定，见我一面难上难。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00048",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "但不知仙师住在何处？改日也好登门叩访。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00049",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "贫道住在铁冠山，铁冠洞内。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00050",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "但不知此山究在何处？",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00051",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "酒酒酒，一杯就醉饮百斗。一醉睡到千百年，醒来还要饮一口。色色色，美貌佳人惯惹祸。红粉依旧是骷髅，色即是空空即色。财财财，金银珍宝列满台。好行善事积阴德，明去还能暗里来。气气气，忧愁愤怒皆无益。听天由命不妄求，死后焉能游地狱。山山山，山在虚无缥缈间。酒色财气人能解，便是人间一老仙。",
      "text_length": 140
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00052",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "你三番两次，好叫我不耐烦。吾去也！",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00053",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "庄子下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00054",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "仙师不见。现有柬帖一个，待我看来。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00055",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "火火火，风火二字实难躲，我今若要说与你，又有何人说与我。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00056",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "呵哈哈呀！仙师言语十分深奥。来！",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00057",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "院子暗上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00058",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "院子"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00059",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "现有印信一颗交付与你，你老爷出衙另有公干。改衣更换。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00060",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "白俭换衣。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00061",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "看仙师去之不远，待我赶上前去便了。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00062",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "他说的言和语十分奥妙，我心中好一似冷水来浇。七品郎官不要了，一心要想入山高。弃却红尘免烦恼，",
      "text_length": 46
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00063",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众衙役"
      ],
      "text": "太爷敢是疯了？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00064",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "两旁衙役闹吵吵。夺过了大板将尔来打，",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00065",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "白俭打，众人同下。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00066",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "庄子上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00067",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "劝人要行善，行善成佛到西天。劝人莫行恶，行恶难逃奈河边。为人在世上，凡事忍为先。村中有一汉，性情甚强悍。专恃血气勇，每每起争端。一言就翻脸，把人打伤残。四邻地保到，拉去到当官。先打四十板，然后收在监。每日受困苦，每夜受熬煎。老母去探监，相见泪不干。妻子去送饭，禁卒把他拦。三餐不得饭，夜夜不得眠。终日盼大赦，皇恩赦出监。一家见了面，痛哭了一番。当日若能忍，焉有此祸端。凡事皆须忍，忍即免了难。一忍少苦恼，二忍少愁烦。任凭人笑骂，唾面要自干。诸事皆忍耐，便是一神仙。",
      "text_length": 232
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00068",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "劝世人行善事皆要学好，这忍耐两个字最为高。叹人生到百年终有老，",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00069",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "师傅慢走！弟子赶来了。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00070",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "万事皆空，一笔勾消。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00071",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "白俭上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00072",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "急急走来急急跑，又只见师傅坐土壕。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00073",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "参见师傅。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00074",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "你来赶来作甚？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00075",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "弟子要求师傅收留，入山修道。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00076",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "你要入山修道，你可舍得红尘世界？",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00077",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "舍得。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00078",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "可舍得妻子家属？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00079",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "舍得。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00080",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "你要拜我为师，须要受我之戒。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00081",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "弟子情愿受戒。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00082",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "来来来，这里有包裹行囊，你替为师背在身上。与我头前引路。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00083",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "出家人还有这样苦楚么？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00084",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "这苦还在后头呢。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00085",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "我这里吹法气把红光来罩，划一座深坑独木朽桥。回头来再把那白俭叫，到前面探看路一条。",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00086",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "遵命。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00087",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄原板",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "适才间红日当头照，一瞬时黑暗里看不清分毫。拨开了荒草忙把路找，",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00088",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 88,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00089",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 89,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "万丈深坑一朽桥。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00090",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 90,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "启师傅，前面均是万丈深坑，只有一独木朽桥。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00091",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 91,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "既然有桥，你站在桥上，看看可能行走过去？",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00092",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 92,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "看那木桥已朽坏多年，只怕就是禽兽雀鸟，也难走过。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00093",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 93,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "为师叫你前去，你只管看来。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00094",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 94,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "哦。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00095",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 95,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "先前令我把路找，如今又叫我踏朽桥。将足搭在桥梁上，",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00096",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 96,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "哎呀！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00097",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 97,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "跌将下去我的命难逃。回头便把师傅叫，这出家不如作官高。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00098",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 98,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "启师傅，弟子不愿出家，仍要回去作官去了。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00099",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 99,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "你即不愿出家，你就与我走，与我去。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00100",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 100,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "两冲。虎形上，扑白俭，白俭跌僵尸，虎形下。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00101",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 101,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "二黄导板",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "一霎时吓得我三魂飘散，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00102",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 102,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "又只见师傅在面前。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00103",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 103,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "白俭"
      ],
      "text": "适才弟子遇见一只猛虎，将我吞吃腹内，为何弟子还在此地？",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00104",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 104,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "庄子"
      ],
      "text": "白俭，你的凡身已经脱去。现时已登仙界了。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "01014013_e00105",
      "play_id": "01014013",
      "scene_id": "01014013_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 105,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
